Tony Gardner sizes up the animatronic Alien Queen and Sigourney Weaver puppets at Doug Beswick Studios while the puppets were under construction for James Cameron's "Aliens."
"ALIENS" crew member Tony Gardner, responsible for the film's "Chest Burster" stage of the alien, is seen here inspecting the first skin cast from the creature's body mold.
